window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>War is hell, especially when you’re surrounded by enemies.</p> <p>With the king of Garenland dead and the people eager for revenge, Otto and Wolfric turn their sights north to Garenland’s ancient enemy Straken.</p> <p>The Northern Army marches into enemy territory, while back in the capital, Otto rushes to train as many war wizards as he can.</p> <p>Outside forces refuse to leave them alone, and Otto is forced to deal with an ever-growing array of foes, unreliable allies, and an enemy that will do anything to see Garenland fall.</p> <p>Can Otto overcome threats, both internal and external, to bring the war to a victorious close?</p>"; 
